---
// src/components/sections/Problem.astro
---

<section id="problem" class="relative z-10 bg-[#fff5f5] border-y border-red-100/50">
  <div class="max-w-[1380px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:px-16 md:py-[100px]">
    
    <!-- Section Heading -->
    <div class="text-left max-w-5xl mb-16">
      <span class="eyebrow block mb-3">— THE PROBLEM</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading mb-4">
        When the log line isn't there, the AI guesses.<br class="hidden sm:inline" />
        <span class="accent">And so do you.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="body-text">
        AI writes more of your code every month. The dev debugging it didn't write it. The agent didn't predict where it would fail. So when something breaks, the variable you actually need to see was never logged — and neither of you has a way to find out what happened without redeploying.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="rounded-none border border-red-100/80 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[180px]">
        <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-brand-primary tracking-tight mb-4">3-4h</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          Average time spent searching through scattered log lines to manually reconstruct application state.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="rounded-none border border-red-100/80 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[180px]">
        <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-brand-primary tracking-tight mb-4">45m</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
          Average time required for a developer to re-enter the deep flow zone after a context switch.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="rounded-none border border-red-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[180px] ring-2 ring-brand-primary/10">
        <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-brand-primary tracking-tight mb-4">10m</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed">
          Total time spent identifying, tracing variables, and deploying a permanent patch using Hyperprobe.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
